<h2>Rendering price guide</h2><p>Surrey labour and access sit slightly above the national average. These are typical installed prices (materials, labour and standard scaffolding):</p>
<table><thead><tr><th>System</th><th>Per m² installed</th><th>Best for</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr><td>Acrylic / coloured</td><td>£40–£85</td><td>Bold colour, flexible, pebbledash refresh</td></tr>
<tr><td>Monocouche</td><td>£45–£90</td><td>Durable through-coloured finish</td></tr>
<tr><td>K-Rend / Weber</td><td>£55–£80</td><td>Through-colour + self-cleaning</td></tr>
<tr><td>Silicone</td><td>£60–£120</td><td>Premium, self-cleaning, breathable</td></tr>
<tr><td>EWI + render</td><td>from £100</td><td>Insulation + new facade in one</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>What a typical house costs</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Approx wall area</th><th>Typical total</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr><td>Terraced / bungalow</td><td>60–90 m²</td><td>£3,000–£8,000</td></tr>
<tr><td>Semi-detached</td><td>90–150 m²</td><td>£5,000–£11,000</td></tr>
<tr><td>Detached</td><td>150–300 m²</td><td>£9,000–£16,500+</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<p style="font-size:.85rem;color:#888">Guide figures including scaffolding. Your exact price depends on wall area, height/access, render system and the condition of the existing surface (hacking off old render or extensive making-good adds labour). We confirm everything in a fixed written quote after a free survey.</p>
<h2>What's included</h2><ul><li>Free survey and substrate assessment</li><li>Scaffold, beads, fibreglass mesh and base coat</li><li>Through-coloured topcoat in your chosen colour and finish</li><li>Site cleared and left tidy</li><li>Workmanship guarantee + manufacturer warranty on approved systems</li></ul>
